			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1384165">
									

<p>Nah, it's good as it is.<br />
This isn't an SCP, it's just a bit of creepypasta, and well&#8230; the descriptions, though a bit flowery, aren't bad.</p>
<p>Besides the article is done in a very, very win way.<br />
The first win moment is when she found the placenta super-tasty.. i guess it makes some sort of vague sense biologically, why such behaviour would be rewarded as it's unsanitary keeping it around.</p>
<p>Second was when she actually disliked her kid's flesh, and snapped back - just before that i was expecting an exercise in cannibalism and meh.</p>

