<p>Very creepy! I had chills halfway through and they almost didn't stop! The only thing is that it reminds me of the episode of It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia, where Dee and Charlie eat squirrel meat and think it's human meat and get a &quot;craving&quot; for it. That thought actually made me chuckle.</p>

