<p>This was very effective. Two things: there's a &quot;bit she wouldn’t let go&quot;, and my inner writer recoils from &quot;rictus grin&quot;. I think there's also a paragraph missing a space after.</p>
<p>Today I learned that the only thing worse than reading about a woman eating her placenta is reading about her <em>enjoying</em> it.</p>

